        "description": "<p>The Backend Designer allows you to create your own Color Scheme for your WordPress admin panel with <strong>Live-Preview.<\/strong> Also you can customize the Login screen uploading your own logo and style it with your favorite colors. So helpful to make client projects unique!<\/p>\n<p><strong>See it in action!<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=NZuNEaZnu1M\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Backend Designer &#8211; Video<\/a><\/p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/NZuNEaZnu1M?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"><\/iframe><\/span>\n<p><strong>Features<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create your own design for the WordPress Backend. It\u00b4s so easy.<\/li>\n<li>Customize the WordPress Login screen. Upload your own logo and style it with your favorite colors.<\/li>\n<li>Upload an awesome background image to your login screen to make it very unique.<\/li>\n<li>Set your favorite font family for your backend.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Live Preview:<\/strong> You can see the color changes while changing.<\/li>\n<li>You have the possibility to enable your created color scheme globally for all users.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>It\u00b4s very fast. Style your backend in 2 minutes and make it awesome!<\/li>\n<li>Preview your changes live before you save them.<\/li>\n<li>Your WordPress Backend will look very unique. Be creative!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Install the plugin.<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin.<\/li>\n<li>Open the new menu item (Appearance -&gt; Backend Designer) and start with your styling!<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "faq": "<p>You have issues or questions? Please use the support section, I will try my best to solve your problems quickly!<\/p>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Security Fixes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Bug Fixing<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New features:<\/li>\n<li>Custom font for backend views. More are coming soon!<\/li>\n<li>Custom background image for login screen<\/li>\n<li>Some bug fixes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Translation: German<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Little Bug fix.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/backend-designer\/assets\/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1295681\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/backend-designer\/assets\/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1295681\" alt=\"Nice and clean Backend Panel to have a lot of fun. :-)\"><\/a><p>Nice and clean Backend Panel to have a lot of fun. :-)<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/backend-designer\/assets\/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1295681\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/backend-designer\/assets\/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1295681\" alt=\"Create your own design for the wordpress backend and play with your favorite colors.\"><\/a><p>Create your own design for the wordpress backend and play with your favorite colors.<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/backend-designer\/assets\/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1295681\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/backend-designer\/assets\/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1295681\" alt=\"Cuszomize the Login Screen with your own logo and custom colors.\"><\/a><p>Cuszomize the Login Screen with your own logo and custom colors.<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/backend-designer\/assets\/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=1295681\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/backend-designer\/assets\/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=1295681\" alt=\"Make it unique.\"><\/a><p>Make it unique.<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Simple Plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/kenmundell\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/84e01884014cbdc4ecb39bbee63ac484?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/84e01884014cbdc4ecb39bbee63ac484?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/kenmundell\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kenmundell<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 26, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Really like how simple your plugin is to use and make changes. Is it possible to add a little more customization? Like adding more options that can be customized, links, backgrounds, etc. and possibly a spot to add custom css for the admin for a couple things that aren't available?<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Love it<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<di